      "activity_c": [
        {
          "id": "t_14_1",
          "text": "Good morning, sir. The bakery floor is a bit noisy today.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_1.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_2",
          "text": "I think one of the mixers is making a strange sound.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_2.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_3",
          "text": "Morning, Ruwan. I’m the maintenance person here, so I’ve been checking the machines since 7 a.m.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_3.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_4",
          "text": "Yes, I heard that sound too.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_4.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_5",
          "text": "When I checked it earlier, the belt was a bit loose.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_5.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_6",
          "text": "I tightened it, but it is still making a light knocking noise.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_6.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_7",
          "text": "I also noticed the dough proofer door.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_7.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_8",
          "text": "Yesterday it was fine, but this morning it is not closing properly.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_8.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_9",
          "text": "Yes, one of the hinges was bent.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_9.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_10",
          "text": "I adjusted it, but we might need to replace the rubber seal later.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_10.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_11",
          "text": "Can you also look at the cooling rack?",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_11.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_12",
          "text": "The trainees are cleaning it now, but yesterday it collapsed slightly on one side.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_12.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_13",
          "text": "I inspected it.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_13.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_14",
          "text": "One screw was missing, so I added a new one.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_14.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_15",
          "text": "Tell the trainees to be careful when they move it.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_15.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_16",
          "text": "By the way, the oven temperature display was blurry last night.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_16.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_17",
          "text": "We cleaned the panel, but it is still dim.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_17.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_18",
          "text": "I tested the wiring in the morning.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_18.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_19",
          "text": "Everything was fine, but the bulb might be failing.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_19.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_20",
          "text": "I ordered a replacement. It should arrive this evening.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_20.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_21",
          "text": "Another thing, yesterday we washed all the mixing bowls and stored them on the top rack.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_21.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_22",
          "text": "This morning, a tray fell when I pulled it.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_22.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_23",
          "text": "That rack was unstable for a long time.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_23.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_24",
          "text": "I repaired two joints, but we might need a full replacement.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_24.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_25",
          "text": "I will place an order for a new one.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_25.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_26",
          "text": "Can you check the packaging machine too?",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_26.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_27",
          "text": "It is shaking more than usual.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_27.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_28",
          "text": "I checked it briefly.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_28.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_29",
          "text": "The motor was dusty, so I cleaned it.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_29.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_30",
          "text": "But I’ll inspect the bearings after lunch.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_30.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_31",
          "text": "Thanks, sir. We can’t start packing until it’s stable.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_31.mp3"
        },
        {
          "id": "t_14_32",
          "text": "No worries. I’ll finish it by 11 a.m.",
          "audio": "assets/audio/t_14_32.mp3"
        }
      ],
